Interface MVGraphElement

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MVComponent, MVEdge, MVGraph, MVMetadata
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MVEngineComponent, MVEngineEdge, MVEngineGraph, MVEngineMetadata

    public interface MVGraphElement
    This is general model view to a graph element. This model view is used by MetadataPropagationResolver.
